ients and colleagues.\nTime management skills and the ability to cope with several projects at a time.\nAccuracy and attention to detail when finalizing designs.\nBeing open to feedback and willing to make changes to your designs.\nEffective networking skills to build contacts.\n\nRelevant subjects for graphic design work include those that involve visual arts. In:-\n\nDesign &Animation Tools\nAdobe Photoshop\nAdobe Illustrator\nAdobe In Design\nAdobe Flash\nMacromedia Free Hand\nKalka for Arabic Calligraphy\nAuthoring Tools\nAdobe Captivate\nArticulate Storyline\nAdobe Edge Animate\nVideo/Sound Editor\nAdobe Audition\nAdobe After Effect\n','2023-09-01',2,0,2,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,5,'Experienced (Non-Manager)','Bachelor\'s Degree','Dolf',NULL),('Quality control','Egypt','Cairo','Heliopolis','● Inspect buildings and the surrounding environment for signs of pest infestation● Determine the type of treatment needed to eliminate pests● Take the required measurement of the area in need of treatment● Estimate the cost of services rendered to clients or customers● Use different pest control methods such as the setting of traps or baits to remove or kill pests● Apply pesticide safely in buildings or structures and the surrounding environment','Proven work experience as a Pest Control Technician or similar role Must possess physical stamina and be able to withstand harsh conditions Ability to stand for an extended period of time and work in uncomfortable environments Must be detailed oriented and be able to follow detailed instructions in applying pesticide to avoid harm to the client and self Must possess good customer service skills and be customer-focused Strong ability to keep good records of hours worked, chemicals used and payment collected High school diploma or equivalent preferred','2023-09-01',14,0,2,5,NULL,NULL,1,3,'Experienced (Non-Manager)',NULL,'Dolf',NULL),('Data Manager / Documents Controller (m/f)','Saudi Arabia','Riyadh','','The Dornier Groupstands for innovative